show.title: Wake Up, Dad! Wedding Time
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/BqDxsq
show.description: Laila is kicked out of her home after an unexpected pregnancy. Years later, the father of her child, Roman, shows up, revealing he is the world's richest man. To get medical treatment for her son, Laila agrees to a contractual marriage with Roman. However, as they get to know each other, they gradually break the contract and fall in love.
